article_title: Marco Rubio's Healthcare Plan Absolutely Does Not Contain An Individual Mandate

article_metadata.description: Michael Cannon of the Cato Institute has accused Marco Rubio of having an individual mandate in his healthcare plan. He is not only being inaccurate, he is irresponsible to do so.
article_metadata.author: Ryan Ellis
